adding-top:10px;\">\n<table style=\"background:transparent; width:100%; text-align:center;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">\n<div style=\"width:150px; height:100px; margin:4px; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; -moz-box-shadow: 4px 4px 6px #888; -webkit-box-shadow: 4px 4px 6px #888; box-shadow: 4px 4px 6px #888;\"><div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\"><img alt=\"Locator map Westeros in Known world.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/00/Locator_map_Westeros_in_Known_world.svg/150px-Locator_map_Westeros_in_Known_world.svg.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"100\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/00/Locator_map_Westeros_in_Known_world.svg/225px-Locator_map_Westeros_in_Known_world.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/00/Locator_map_Westeros_in_Known_world.svg/300px-Locator_map_Westeros_in_Known_world.svg.png 2x\" /></a></div><div><a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></div></div>\n<div style=\"width:150px; height:100px; margin:4px; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; -moz-box-shadow: 4px 4px 6px #888; -webkit-box-shadow: 4px 4px 6px #888; box-shadow: 4px 4px 6px #888;\"><div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\"><img alt=\"Locator map Essos in Known world.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/de/Locator_map_Essos_in_Known_world.svg/150px-Locator_map_Essos_in_Known_world.svg.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"100\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/de/Locator_map_Essos_in_Known_world.svg/225px-Locator_map_Essos_in_Known_world.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/de/Locator_map_Essos_in_Known_world.svg/300px-Locator_map_Essos_in_Known_world.svg.png 2x\" /></a></div><div><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a></div></div>\n<div style=\"width:150px; height:100px; margin:4px; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; -moz-box-shadow: 4px 4px 6px #888; -webkit-box-shadow: 4px 4px 6px #888; box-shadow: 4px 4px 6px #888;\"><div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Sothoryos\" title=\"Sothoryos\"><img alt=\"Locator map Sothoryos in Known world.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d4/Locator_map_Sothoryos_in_Known_world.svg/150px-Locator_map_Sothoryos_in_Known_world.svg.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"100\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d4/Locator_map_Sothoryos_in_Known_world.svg/225px-Locator_map_Sothoryos_in_Known_world.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d4/Locator_map_Sothoryos_in_Known_world.svg/300px-Locator_map_Sothoryos_in_Known_world.svg.png 2x\" /></a></div><div><a href=\"/index.php/Sothoryos\" title=\"Sothoryos\">Sothoryos</a></div></div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div> <div style=\"text-align:left; position:relative; left:0px; top:2px; margin:0;\"><img alt=\"Beige-bg rounded.png\" src=\"/images/7/70/Beige-bg_rounded.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"25\" />\n<div style=\"position:absolute; left:15px; top:2px;\"><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold; border-bottom:none; font-size:130%; padding:.15em .4em; margin-top: -0.15em;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Continents\">Continents</span></h2></div></div>\n<div style=\"padding-left:15px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:10px;\">\n<ul><li><b><a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></b>: Located in the far west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a>, Westeros extends southwards from the northern polar icecap for approximately 3,000 miles. The <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>, a colossal fortification which stretches for 300 miles, separates the lands north of the Wall from the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>, a political entity that unifies the rest of the continent. This realm south of the Wall is divided into nine constituent regions or provinces.<br /><br /><b><a href=\"/index.php/Regions_of_Westeros\" title=\"Regions of Westeros\">Regions</a></b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">Beyond the Wall</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>.</li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<hr />\n<ul><li><b><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a></b>: Separated from Westeros by the narrow sea, Essos extends eastwards for many thousands of miles. It is larger than Westeros but less densely populated. The western edge of the continent is controlled by the nine <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>, whilst the city-states of <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> are located in the south-central region. Much of the continental interior known as the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a> is ruled by the tribal warriors known as the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a>. Further east is <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> and the fabled <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a>. Western and eastern Essos are separated by the <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a>, east of which are <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a>, legendary <a href=\"/index.php/Asshai\" title=\"Asshai\">Asshai</a> and the forbidding <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Lands\" title=\"Shadow Lands\">Shadow Lands</a>.<br /><br /><b>Regions</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Red_waste\" title=\"Red waste\">Red waste</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_peninsula\" title=\"Valyrian peninsula\">Valyrian peninsula</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Further_East\" title=\"Further East\">Further East</a>.</li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<hr />\n<ul><li><b><a href=\"/index.php/Sothoryos\" title=\"Sothoryos\">Sothoryos</a></b>: Relatively little known, Sothoryos is located south of Essos, on the far side of the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Sea\" title=\"Summer Sea\">Summer Sea</a>. It is a large continent consisting of deserts and jungles. It is said to be a haven for plagues and dangerous animals, and has not been explored much beyond the northern coastal regions and the <a href=\"/index.php/Basilisk_Isles\" title=\"Basilisk Isles\">Basilisk Isles</a>.<br /><br /><b>Regions</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Naath\" title=\"Naath\">Naath</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Tears\" title=\"Isle of Tears\">Isle of Tears</a> <b>·</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Basilisk_Point\" title=\"Basilisk Point\">Basilisk Point</a></li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n</div> <div style=\"text-align:left; position:relative; left:0px; top:2px; margin:0;\"><img alt=\"Beige-bg rounded.png\" src=\"/images/7/70/Beige-bg_rounded.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"25\" />\n<div style=\"position:absolute; left:15px; top:2px;\"><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold; border-bottom:none; font-size:130%; padding:.15em .4em; margin-top: -0.15em;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Official_Maps\">Official Maps</span></h2></div></div>\n<div style=\"padding-left:15px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:10px;\">\n<p><i><b><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></b></i>:\n</p>\n<div style=\"colum